$ Perl module DBI: selectcol_arrayref

By default, the method `selectcol_arrayref` returns a ref to a list containing the elements of the first column of
the result set of the select statement:
gh|PerlModules|/DBI/selectcol_arrayref.pl||

Multiple columns *can* be selected, however, the result set is not row or column based at all:
gh|PerlModules|/DBI/selectcol_arrayref-multiple-columns.pl||

sa:
  → development/languages/Perl/modules/DBI/select_all

  → development/languages/Perl/modules/DBI
